<view class="match-page data-v-edf061ca"><view class="hero-section data-v-edf061ca"><view class="hero-badge data-v-edf061ca">Smart Match</view><text class="hero-title data-v-edf061ca">为你推荐更适合长期坚持的健身搭子</text><text class="hero-desc data-v-edf061ca"> 推荐会综合训练目标、偏好时段、训练场景和监督需求，让第一次发起邀请更有把握。 </text><view class="hero-meta data-v-edf061ca"><view class="hero-chip data-v-edf061ca"><text class="chip-label data-v-edf061ca">推荐数量</text><text class="chip-value data-v-edf061ca">{{a}}</text></view><view class="hero-chip data-v-edf061ca"><text class="chip-label data-v-edf061ca">当前状态</text><text class="chip-value data-v-edf061ca">{{b}}</text></view></view></view><view wx:if="{{c}}" class="loading-panel data-v-edf061ca"><view class="loading-spinner data-v-edf061ca"></view><text class="loading-title data-v-edf061ca">正在生成匹配推荐</text><text class="loading-copy data-v-edf061ca">结合你的档案信息筛选更合适的训练伙伴</text></view><block wx:else><view wx:if="{{d}}" class="section-card data-v-edf061ca"><view class="section-head data-v-edf061ca"><view class="data-v-edf061ca"><text class="section-title data-v-edf061ca">推荐结果</text><text class="section-subtitle data-v-edf061ca">优先展示更适合立即开始训练配对的用户</text></view><text class="section-count data-v-edf061ca">{{e}} 位搭子</text></view><view class="match-list data-v-edf061ca"><view wx:for="{{f}}" wx:for-item="item" wx:key="s" class="match-card data-v-edf061ca"><view class="card-top data-v-edf061ca"><view class="match-avatar data-v-edf061ca"><image wx:if="{{item.a}}" src="{{item.b}}" class="avatar-image data-v-edf061ca" mode="aspectFill" binderror="{{item.c}}"/><text wx:else class="avatar-text data-v-edf061ca">{{item.d}}</text></view><view class="match-main data-v-edf061ca"><view class="name-row data-v-edf061ca"><text class="match-name data-v-edf061ca">{{item.e}}</text><view class="score-pill data-v-edf061ca"><text class="score-pill-text data-v-edf061ca">{{item.f}}%</text></view></view><text class="match-reason data-v-edf061ca">{{item.g}}</text><view class="score-track data-v-edf061ca"><view class="score-fill data-v-edf061ca" style="{{'width:' + item.h}}"></view></view></view></view><view class="tag-group data-v-edf061ca"><text wx:if="{{item.i}}" class="tag-item goal data-v-edf061ca">{{item.j}}</text><text wx:if="{{item.k}}" class="tag-item time data-v-edf061ca">{{item.l}}</text><text wx:if="{{item.m}}" class="tag-item scene data-v-edf061ca">{{item.n}}</text><text wx:if="{{item.o}}" class="tag-item mode data-v-edf061ca">{{item.p}}</text></view><view class="card-actions data-v-edf061ca"><view class="action-btn secondary data-v-edf061ca" bindtap="{{item.q}}"><text class="action-btn-text secondary-text data-v-edf061ca">完善档案</text></view><view class="action-btn primary data-v-edf061ca" bindtap="{{item.r}}"><text class="action-btn-text data-v-edf061ca">去发起组队</text></view></view></view></view></view><view wx:else class="empty-card data-v-edf061ca"><view class="empty-icon data-v-edf061ca">配</view><text class="empty-title data-v-edf061ca">暂时还没有合适的匹配结果</text><text class="empty-desc data-v-edf061ca"> 可以先补充你的目标、训练时间和训练场景，系统会给出更准确的推荐。 </text><view class="empty-actions data-v-edf061ca"><view class="action-btn primary data-v-edf061ca" bindtap="{{g}}"><text class="action-btn-text data-v-edf061ca">去完善档案</text></view><view class="action-btn secondary data-v-edf061ca" bindtap="{{h}}"><text class="action-btn-text secondary-text data-v-edf061ca">重新匹配</text></view></view></view><view class="refresh-bar data-v-edf061ca"><view class="refresh-btn data-v-edf061ca" bindtap="{{i}}"><text class="refresh-text data-v-edf061ca">刷新推荐</text></view></view></block></view>